[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":660},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Freact\u002F20221003\u002F1202137007\u002F":3,"page:\u002Freact\u002F20221003\u002F1202137007\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Freact\u002F20221003\u002F1202137007\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Freact\u002F20221003\u002F1202137007\u002F":635,"related:\u002Freact\u002F20221003\u002F1202137007\u002F":644},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F03\u002Flearn-react-19-create-react-app-cra-setup\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":616,"date":617,"description":18,"extension":618,"lang":619,"meta":620,"navigation":457,"path":621,"readingMinutes":622,"seo":623,"standalone":624,"stem":625,"tags":626,"tldr":632,"updated":632,"url":633,"__hash__":634},"content\u002F終究都要學 React 何不現在學呢？\u002F19-終究都要學-React-何不現在學呢？-React-CRA-CRA-建立.md","終究都要學 React 何不現在學呢？ - React CRA - CRA 建立 - (19)","1202137007",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":610},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,32,35,55,58,61,91,94,97,114,117,139,150,153,168,175,182,192,198,201,205,208,326,329,343,352,355,365,372,561,575,582,588,591,594,597,606],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"這一章節開始我們將會進入全新的章節，也就是 React CRA 章節，從這個章節開始也會慢慢減少在 CodePen 上的使用，而是開始進入實戰常見得開發環境。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"什麼是-cra","什麼是 CRA？",[16,24,25],{},"其實 CRA 是 Create React App 的縮寫，就跟 VAR 是 Vue、Angular、React 的縮寫一樣(取自大寫部分)。",[16,27,28],{},"透過 CRA 可以非常快速的幫我們準備好開發環境，如果你有使用過 Vue CLI 的話，那麼概念就跟 Vue CLI 一樣，那麼使用 CRA 好處在於，你可以不用從頭開始學 Webpack，叫你從 Webpack 一路自幹設置到一個可以開發的開發環境出來是非常花時間的，更不用說過程中你還要先學會 Webpack 跟一推東西。",[16,30,31],{},"那麼該如何使用 CRA 呢？在說明使用 CRA 之前如果你是初次使用而沒有安裝過 Node.js 的話，我會建議你安裝一下 Node.js，因為 CRA 是基於 Node.js 製作的，所以你必須先安裝 Node.js 才能使用 CRA。",[16,33,34],{},"這邊我也推薦你可以參考我以下文章安裝一下 nvm",[36,37,38,48],"ul",{},[39,40,41],"li",{},[42,43,47],"a",{"href":44,"rel":45},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fnodejs\u002F20200107\u002F3738078915\u002F",[46],"nofollow","Windows 10 安裝並使用 nvm 切換 NodeJS 版本",[39,49,50],{},[42,51,54],{"href":52,"rel":53},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fnodejs\u002F20200124\u002F3404456418\u002F",[46],"Mac OS X 安裝 nvm",[16,56,57],{},"nvm 簡單來講就是 Node.js 管理工具，因為我們在實戰開發上時常會切換 Node.js 版本，所以會建議安裝與使用 nvm 會較好。",[16,59,60],{},"最後這邊我也附上 nvm 常見問題給予參考",[36,62,63,70,77,84],{},[39,64,65],{},[42,66,69],{"href":67,"rel":68},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20220127\u002F999847254\u002F",[46],"解決 Windows nvm 出現 Access is denied 或 exit status 145 問題",[39,71,72],{},[42,73,76],{"href":74,"rel":75},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220615\u002F3487431106\u002F",[46],"npm WARN config global --global, --local are deprecated. Use --location=global instead 解決方式",[39,78,79],{},[42,80,83],{"href":81,"rel":82},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20210603\u002F2683176705\u002F",[46],"解決 Mac 輸入指令出現 command not found: npm 問題",[39,85,86],{},[42,87,90],{"href":88,"rel":89},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190801\u002F449913843\u002F",[46],"無法辨識 'XXX' 詞彙是否為 Cmdlet、函數、指令檔或可執行程式的名稱",[16,92,93],{},"希望以上資訊可以幫助到你順利安裝與使用 nvm。",[16,95,96],{},"接著拉回到原本主題上，我們該如何使用 CRA 呢？非常簡單你只需要打開終端機，輸入以下指令即可",[98,99,104],"pre",{"className":100,"code":101,"language":102,"meta":103,"style":103},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","npx create-react-app example-app\n","cmd","",[105,106,107],"code",{"__ignoreMap":103},[108,109,112],"span",{"class":110,"line":111},"line",1,[108,113,101],{},[16,115,116],{},"過程你可能會遇到這個提示訊息",[98,118,120],{"className":100,"code":119,"language":102,"meta":103,"style":103},"Need to install the following packages:\n  create-react-app\nOk to proceed? (y)\n",[105,121,122,127,133],{"__ignoreMap":103},[108,123,124],{"class":110,"line":111},[108,125,126],{},"Need to install the following packages:\n",[108,128,130],{"class":110,"line":129},2,[108,131,132],{},"  create-react-app\n",[108,134,136],{"class":110,"line":135},3,[108,137,138],{},"Ok to proceed? (y)\n",[16,140,141,142,145,146,149],{},"不用害怕，大膽按下 ",[105,143,144],{},"Y"," 就對了，它只是在跟你說它需要安裝 ",[105,147,148],{},"create-react-app"," 這個包(套件)而已，接下來過程會需要稍微等一下，可能大約幾秒到幾分鐘不等，這一部分完全看網路狀況。",[16,151,152],{},"跑完之後就可以準備輸入以下指令啟動開發環境了",[98,154,156],{"className":100,"code":155,"language":102,"meta":103,"style":103},"cd example-app\nnpm start\n",[105,157,158,163],{"__ignoreMap":103},[108,159,160],{"class":110,"line":111},[108,161,162],{},"cd example-app\n",[108,164,165],{"class":110,"line":129},[108,166,167],{},"npm start\n",[16,169,170,171,174],{},"輸入完 ",[105,172,173],{},"npm start"," 之後，你應該會發現瀏覽器自動打開了，此時你應該會看到一個 React 畫面",[16,176,177],{},[178,179],"img",{"alt":180,"src":181},"Run CRA","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%20Vue%20%E7%9A%84%20React%20Hook%20%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%80%85\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-06-25%2001.05.21.png",[16,183,184,185,188,189,191],{},"如果沒有自動打開的話，你也可以試著自己打開瀏覽器，並在網址列上輸入 ",[105,186,187],{},"http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:3000"," 也是一種方式，如果你發現 ",[105,190,187],{}," 無效的話，就會建議你看一下終端機畫面圈起來的地方",[16,193,194],{},[178,195],{"alt":196,"src":197},"localhost","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%20Vue%20%E7%9A%84%20React%20Hook%20%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%80%85\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_6_25_01_14.png",[16,199,200],{},"這一篇好像有點太少了，所以後面我也稍微補一下 CRA 專案結構。",[12,202,204],{"id":203},"cra-專案結構","CRA 專案結構",[16,206,207],{},"當你建立好後，你的專案結構目前應該是如下：",[36,209,210],{},[39,211,212,215],{},[105,213,214],{},"example-app",[36,216,217,222,227,232,237,242,279],{},[39,218,219],{},[105,220,221],{},"README.md",[39,223,224],{},[105,225,226],{},"node_modules",[39,228,229],{},[105,230,231],{},"package.json",[39,233,234],{},[105,235,236],{},"package-lock.json",[39,238,239],{},[105,240,241],{},".gitignore",[39,243,244,247],{},[105,245,246],{},"public",[36,248,249,254,259,264,269,274],{},[39,250,251],{},[105,252,253],{},"favicon.ico",[39,255,256],{},[105,257,258],{},"index.html",[39,260,261],{},[105,262,263],{},"logo192.png",[39,265,266],{},[105,267,268],{},"logo512.png",[39,270,271],{},[105,272,273],{},"manifest.json",[39,275,276],{},[105,277,278],{},"robots.txt",[39,280,281,284],{},[105,282,283],{},"src",[36,285,286,291,296,301,306,311,316,321],{},[39,287,288],{},[105,289,290],{},"App.css",[39,292,293],{},[105,294,295],{},"App.js",[39,297,298],{},[105,299,300],{},"App.test.js",[39,302,303],{},[105,304,305],{},"index.css",[39,307,308],{},[105,309,310],{},"index.js",[39,312,313],{},[105,314,315],{},"logo.svg",[39,317,318],{},[105,319,320],{},"reportWebVitals.js",[39,322,323],{},[105,324,325],{},"setupTests.js",[16,327,328],{},"而這邊有兩個檔案需要特別注意：",[36,330,331,337],{},[39,332,333,336],{},[105,334,335],{},"public\u002Findex.html"," 頁面注入點",[39,338,339,342],{},[105,340,341],{},"src\u002Findex.js JavaScript"," 進入點",[16,344,345,346,348,349,351],{},"而通常來講我們會調整 ",[105,347,283],{}," 底下的檔案，例如新增資料夾、檔案或是編輯等，而這邊要注意這個 ",[105,350,283],{}," 名字不要隨意更動，因為默認 CRA 會去尋找這個資料夾。",[16,353,354],{},"那你可能會想說「奇怪，這個專案怎麼好像都沒有用什麼工具也可以編譯？它是用 Webpack 嗎？好像都沒看到相關設定檔案？」",[16,356,357,358,360,361,364],{},"沒有錯 CRA 本質就是使用 Webpack，而 CRA 也與 Vue CLI 一樣，相關的 Webpack 都是在 ",[105,359,226],{}," 底下，如果你好奇的話可以看一下 ",[105,362,363],{},"node_modules\u002Freact-scripts"," 裡面就是 CRA 的 Webpack 相關設定，這邊就不額外介紹了。",[16,366,367,368,371],{},"接下來讓我們看一下 ",[105,369,370],{},"src\u002Findex.js"," 現在的內容",[98,373,377],{"className":374,"code":375,"language":376,"meta":103,"style":103},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","import React from 'react';\nimport ReactDOM from 'react-dom\u002Fclient';\nimport '.\u002Findex.css';\nimport App from '.\u002FApp';\nimport reportWebVitals from '.\u002FreportWebVitals';\n\nconst root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));\nroot.render(\n  \u003CReact.StrictMode>\n    \u003CApp \u002F>\n  \u003C\u002FReact.StrictMode>\n);\n\nreportWebVitals();\n","js",[105,378,379,399,413,422,437,452,459,494,506,519,531,541,547,552],{"__ignoreMap":103},[108,380,381,385,389,392,396],{"class":110,"line":111},[108,382,384],{"class":383},"sWyjQ","import",[108,386,388],{"class":387},"sMAXC"," React ",[108,390,391],{"class":383},"from",[108,393,395],{"class":394},"sTRMh"," 'react'",[108,397,398],{"class":387},";\n",[108,400,401,403,406,408,411],{"class":110,"line":129},[108,402,384],{"class":383},[108,404,405],{"class":387}," ReactDOM ",[108,407,391],{"class":383},[108,409,410],{"class":394}," 'react-dom\u002Fclient'",[108,412,398],{"class":387},[108,414,415,417,420],{"class":110,"line":135},[108,416,384],{"class":383},[108,418,419],{"class":394}," '.\u002Findex.css'",[108,421,398],{"class":387},[108,423,425,427,430,432,435],{"class":110,"line":424},4,[108,426,384],{"class":383},[108,428,429],{"class":387}," App ",[108,431,391],{"class":383},[108,433,434],{"class":394}," '.\u002FApp'",[108,436,398],{"class":387},[108,438,440,442,445,447,450],{"class":110,"line":439},5,[108,441,384],{"class":383},[108,443,444],{"class":387}," reportWebVitals ",[108,446,391],{"class":383},[108,448,449],{"class":394}," '.\u002FreportWebVitals'",[108,451,398],{"class":387},[108,453,455],{"class":110,"line":454},6,[108,456,458],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":457},true,"\n",[108,460,462,465,469,472,475,479,482,485,488,491],{"class":110,"line":461},7,[108,463,464],{"class":383},"const",[108,466,468],{"class":467},"sCcAr"," root",[108,470,471],{"class":383}," =",[108,473,474],{"class":387}," ReactDOM.",[108,476,478],{"class":477},"sj_SG","createRoot",[108,480,481],{"class":387},"(document.",[108,483,484],{"class":477},"getElementById",[108,486,487],{"class":387},"(",[108,489,490],{"class":394},"'root'",[108,492,493],{"class":387},"));\n",[108,495,497,500,503],{"class":110,"line":496},8,[108,498,499],{"class":387},"root.",[108,501,502],{"class":477},"render",[108,504,505],{"class":387},"(\n",[108,507,509,512,516],{"class":110,"line":508},9,[108,510,511],{"class":387},"  \u003C",[108,513,515],{"class":514},"sKpQp","React.StrictMode",[108,517,518],{"class":387},">\n",[108,520,522,525,528],{"class":110,"line":521},10,[108,523,524],{"class":387},"    \u003C",[108,526,527],{"class":514},"App",[108,529,530],{"class":387}," \u002F>\n",[108,532,534,537,539],{"class":110,"line":533},11,[108,535,536],{"class":387},"  \u003C\u002F",[108,538,515],{"class":514},[108,540,518],{"class":387},[108,542,544],{"class":110,"line":543},12,[108,545,546],{"class":387},");\n",[108,548,550],{"class":110,"line":549},13,[108,551,458],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":457},[108,553,555,558],{"class":110,"line":554},14,[108,556,557],{"class":477},"reportWebVitals",[108,559,560],{"class":387},"();\n",[16,562,563,564,567,568,571,572,574],{},"基本上很多地方與我們前面練習的很像， ",[105,565,566],{},"import React from 'react';"," 與 ",[105,569,570],{},"import ReactDOM from 'react-dom\u002Fclient';"," 原本是掛在 CDN Global 上的，現在是透過 ",[105,573,384],{}," 引入。",[16,576,577,578,581],{},"那 ",[105,579,580],{},"import '.\u002Findex.css';"," 呢？單純只是引入一個 Global 的樣式。",[16,583,584,587],{},[105,585,586],{},"import App from '.\u002FApp';"," 則是如同我們前面練習的一樣，將元件引入到這個檔案並使用，只是前面章節我們並沒有拆檔案而已。",[16,589,590],{},"因此裡面其實至少有八成程式碼你都認識，所以接下來我下一篇會針對剩下兩成你沒看過的程式碼介紹一下。",[12,592,593],{"id":593},"後記",[16,595,596],{},"本文將會同步更新到我的部落格",[36,598,599],{},[39,600,601],{},[42,602,605],{"href":603,"rel":604},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002F",[46],"是 Ray 不是 Array",[607,608,609],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr